<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>bulkbell - 筋トレやる気サポート</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
      background-color: #b32424;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .container {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: row;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    .content {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 60px 40px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .logo::before {
      content: "🔔 ";
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .buttons {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .button {
      padding: 12px 20px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 6px;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .email-btn {
      background-color: #fff;
      color: #222;
    }
    .line-btn {
      background-color: #00c300;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .image {
      flex: 1;
      background-image: url("../assets/bulkbellman.png");
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center top;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content">
      <div class="logo">BulkBell</div>
      <h1>週に設定した曜日に<br>筋トレのやる気を<br>高めるメッセージをお届け</h1>
      <p>メールアドレスやLINEアカウントを連携して、モチベーションをサポートします</p>
      <div class="buttons">
        <a href="#" class="button email-btn">メールアドレスで連携</a>
        <a href="#" class="button line-btn">LINEアカウントで連携</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="image"></div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>